{%- comment -%}
  Hamburger Menu Component
  -------------
  Renders the complete mobile hamburger menu system including:
  - Toggle button with animated lines
  - Full-screen overlay background
  - Sliding drawer with navigation menu
  - Mega menu submenus and featured content

  Parameters:
  - menu: The menu handle to use for navigation items (required)
      Uses same menu configuration as desktop navigation
  - blocks: Theme section blocks containing mega menu settings (required)
      Each block can configure:
      - Parent menu item to attach mega menu to
      - Up to 3 submenu link lists with optional titles
      - Featured content with image, title and URL
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign menu_handle = menu | default: 'main-menu'
  assign menu_items = linklists[menu_handle].links
-%}

{% render 'new-hamburger-button' %}

{% render 'new-hamburger-drawer', menu: menu_handle, blocks: blocks %}
